data.description:
How about an interest rate from 2021! Welcome to Resort-style living at the Highlands at Dove Mountain. Enjoy breathtaking sunrises, and beautiful moon rises, Catalina & Tortolita Mtn views from this spacious townhome. We have an assumable 2.875% first mortgage! and with as little as 10% down and a purchase money 2nd this one can be yours! Upon qualification, text Allen for details.   The beauty & tranquility of the Sonoran Desert shines through the light & bright kitchen/family room along with the master bdrm. This home features an airy open 2 bdrm 2 bath floor plan,10' ceilings. Upgrades and recent improvements include remodeled upgraded kitchen, including granite countertops all new appliances, new flooring in kitchen, family room, great room, and laundry room. All new raised panel interior door , newer A/C & furnace, (2019), hard wired rolling security shutters @ kitchen/family room, interior solar shades, newer Nuvo H2O salt-free water system, gas fireplace, security screen doors,
a secret storage cabinet inside the house! 
This highly desirable Adult Active (50+) community features a clubhouse, dining, bar, community pool, workout facilities, 18-hole golf course, tennis, pickle ball, and many other 
amenities along with great events. The Highlands at Dove Mountain is conveniently located just minutes from I-10 with nearby shopping, restaurants, parks, walking/hiking trails, 
the prestigious Ritz-Carlton Hotel and so much more. You won't want to miss this one....Move -in Ready! Seller is Motivated.
